data.description: 3-bedroom, 2-bath residence in St. Clair Shores. This gem boasts a spacious Master Bedroom with walk-in closets, deluxe bathrooms with double sinks and ceramic tile, and a modern kitchen with a movable island. Enjoy the convenience of first-floor laundry, hardwood floors, and a bay window. Stay comfortable with AC and a new hot water heater. The property includes a 2.5 car garage, patio with brick pavers leading to a winterized in-ground pool, and six ceiling fans. Located in the South Lake School District. Don't miss the chance to call this your home sweet home!
